Invocation Name: w. c. d. i. radio
des:
"WCDI Blazing the airwaves with the Classics that made metal, serving up mega-doses of Black Sabbath, Judas Priest and Iron Maiden. The epic shreddage continues with the 80's reign of Ozzy, Dio, and Dokken as well as Hair Metal glory from Motley Crue, Def Leppard and Twisted Sister.

We mix in newer riff lords like Avenged Sevenfold, Ghost and Greta Van Fleet along with the leading lights of 90's metal Pantera, Slipknot and Megadeth. Gnarly riffs, face-melting solos, banshee wails - it's all here 24-7."
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
